                                listenerd

Python daemon listening for AMQP messages. Necessery files to create 
debian (deb) package are included in the debian folder.

Features:
  
  -- debian package installs listenerd script in /etc/init.d/
  -- Python modules are installed in site-packages
  -- daemon configuation is located in /etc 
  -- script can be run in X clones
  -- each clone has PID file located in /var/run
  -- debian rules file determines which Python versions are installed
     in the OS
  -- daemon uses Python logging module to log to syslog

